        "f\\left( \\mathbf{x} \\right)  =10n + \\displaystyle \\sum^{n}_{i=1} \\left[ x^{2}_{i}-10\\cos \\left( 2\\pi x_{i}\\right)  \\right] \\tag{6.12}\n",
        "$$\n",
