        "f\\left( \\mathbf{x} \\right)  =\\sum^{n-1}_{i=1} \\left( a-x_{i-1}\\right)^{2}  +b\\left( x_{i}-x^{2}_{i-1}\\right)^{2}  +c \\tag{6.106}\n",
